   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The 3rd year of Imperator Caesar Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Augustus and Imperator Caesar Lucius Aurelius Verus Augustus. Work done on the dikes for the same 3rd year, (2nd hand) Payni 23 till 27, at the new sluice gate, on behalf of Tebtunis, (3rd hand) Mieus son of Marepsemis son of Petesouchos, his mother being Senharmais. (4th hand) I, Sokrates, have signed.</ab>
